        "explanation": "Explanation:\nTest case 111: There are 666 permutations we can form by filling in the zeros:\n\n[3,1,2,5,6,8,7,4][3, 1, 2, 5, 6, 8, 7, 4][3,1,2,5,6,8,7,4] with a value of \u22233\u22121\u2223+\u22232\u22125\u2223+\u22236\u22128\u2223+\u22237\u22124\u2223=10|3-1| + |2-5| + |6-8| + |7-4| = 10\u22233\u22121\u2223+\u22232\u22125\u2223+\u22236\u22128\u2223+\u22237\u22124\u2223=10.\n[3,1,7,5,6,8,2,4][3, 1, 7, 5, 6, 8, 2, 4][3,1,7,5,6,8,2,4] with a value of \u22233\u22121\u2223+\u22237\u22125\u2223+\u22236\u22128\u2223+\u22232\u22124\u2223=8|3-1| + |7-5| + |6-8| + |2-4| = 8\u22233\u22121\u2223+\u22237\u22125\u2223+\u22236\u22128\u2223+\u22232\u22124\u2223=8.\n[3,2,1,5,6,8,7,4][3, 2, 1, 5, 6, 8, 7, 4][3,2,1,5,6,8,7,4] with a value of \u22233\u22122\u2223+\u22231\u22125\u2223+\u22236\u22128\u2223+\u22237\u22124\u2223=10|3-2| + |1-5| + |6-8| + |7-4| = 10\u22233\u22122\u2223+\u22231\u22125\u2223+\u22236\u22128\u2223+\u22237\u22124\u2223=10.\n[3,2,7,5,6,8,1,4][3, 2, 7, 5, 6, 8, 1, 4][3,2,7,5,6,8,1,4] with a value of \u22233\u22122\u2223+\u22237\u22125\u2223+\u22236\u22128\u2223+\u22231\u22124\u2223=8|3-2| + |7-5| + |6-8| + |1-4| = 8\u22233\u22122\u2223+\u22237\u22125\u2223+\u22236\u22128\u2223+\u22231\u22124\u2223=8.\n[3,7,1,5,6,8,2,4][3, 7, 1, 5, 6, 8, 2, 4][3,7,1,5,6,8,2,4] with a value of \u22233\u22127\u2223+\u22231\u22125\u2223+\u22236\u22128\u2223+\u22232\u22124\u2223=12|3-7| + |1-5| + |6-8| + |2-4| = 12\u22233\u22127\u2223+\u22231\u22125\u2223+\u22236\u22128\u2223+\u22232\u22124\u2223=12.\n[3,7,2,5,6,8,1,4][3, 7, 2, 5, 6, 8, 1, 4][3,7,2,5,6,8,1,4] with a value of \u22233\u22127\u2223+\u22232\u22125\u2223+\u22236\u22128\u2223+\u22231\u22124\u2223=12|3-7| + |2-5| + |6-8| + |1-4| = 12\u22233\u22127\u2223+\u22232\u22125\u2223+\u22236\u22128\u2223+\u22231\u22124\u2223=12.\n\nThe maximum possible value is 121212, and two permutations attain that maximum.\nTest case 222: There are 242424 ways of filling in the zeros to obtain a permutation; of which it can be verified that 161616 of them attain the maximum possible value of 444.\nTest case 333: There are no zeros, so there's only one permutation (PPP itself) that attains the maximum value."
